author: violetagg
msg: In o.a.tomcat.websocket.server.WsHttpUpgradeHandler.init(WebConnection) if the endpoint is NULL the connection will not be initialized.
Then in o.a.tomcat.websocket.server.WsHttpUpgradeHandler.destroy() the connection should be tested for NULL.
